To install, follow these steps:

1. Open the Teknikum pack compressed file with WinRar.

2. Extract Maps folder, into the main Cstrike directory, If it ask for overwrite anything, take "Yes" This will not remove any other files.

3. Load up Counter-Strike Source, the map will be in the Creat new game, named "de_teknikum" or "aim_teknikum_gym"

4. If you have encountered any bugs or want to give feedback, feel free to send an e-mail.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

If you are going to edit our creation / use for advertisement or add into it; you must give us credit and ask for my permission.
If you are going to make videos / movies of these maps (e.g. make a speed run / play through of the map) feel free but if you are using it in a trailer of some sort, again, please ask for permission and give credit to us for the map.


Have Fun!
